org.openimaj.math.statistics.distribution

Class MultivariateKernelDensityEstimate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.math.statistics.distribution.AbstractMultivariateDistribution
      • org.openimaj.math.statistics.distribution.MultivariateKernelDensityEstimate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultivariateDistribution

    public class MultivariateKernelDensityEstimate
extends AbstractMultivariateDistribution
    A Parzen window kernel density estimate using a univariate kernel and Euclidean distance. Uses a KD-Tree to for efficient neighbour search.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
